files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.CodeAnalysisServiceRunner
files.Summary: Runs Roslyn analysis on a project directory. Loads C# files, builds a compilation and semantic models, and creates a symbol graph via . Tracks files that failed to load in .

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.Enums.EdgeType
files.Summary: Defines the types of edges in the code analysis graph, representing relationships and interactions between nodes such as classes, methods, fields, and properties.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.Enums.NodeType
files.Summary: Defines the types of nodes in the code analysis graph, representing language constructs such as classes, interfaces, methods, constructors, properties, and fields.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Context.GraphContext
files.Summary: Provides controlled access to Roslyn models and the node registry for node/edge builders. Caches syntax roots and hides raw compilation internals.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Context.NodeRegistry
files.Summary: Central registry that maps Roslyn s to graph s. Provides lookup by symbol or by node type, and maintains reverse mappings so builders and analyzers can efficiently query the graph.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.EdgeBuilder.ClassEdgeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds edges for s, including inheritance, implemented interfaces, fields, properties, methods, and constructors.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.EdgeBuilder.ConstructorEdgeBuilder
files.Summary:
Builds edges for s:

  • Structural: adds a HasConstructor edge from the declaring class to the constructor.
  • Behavioral: analyzes object creation expressions inside the constructor body and adds Creates edges to the constructed s.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.EdgeBuilder.EventEdgeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds edges for s, linking them to their declaring class and to any delegate type they reference. Produces , , and edges where applicable.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.EdgeBuilder.FieldEdgeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds edges for s, linking their declared type and any element type (e.g., array or generic element) to the corresponding . Produces and edges.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.EdgeBuilder.IEdgeBuilder
files.Summary: Defines a contract for building edges in the graph for a specific . Each implementation inspects a given and produces outgoing connections based on Roslyn symbols and syntax.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.EdgeBuilder.InterfaceEdgeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds edges for s, capturing inheritance relationships between interfaces (i.e., when an interface extends one or more base interfaces).

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.EdgeBuilder.MethodEdgeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds edges for s, including return type, parameter usage, calls, overrides, object creation, field/property references, and interface implementations.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.EdgeBuilder.PropertyEdgeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds edges for s, including references to fields, usage of class types, and element-type relationships (e.g., arrays, generics). Produces , , and edges.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.GraphBuilder
files.Summary: Builds a graph from Roslyn models. Uses node builders to create class/interface/method/etc. nodes and edge builders to connect them (HasMethod, Calls, Uses, etc.). Stores results in for later analysis.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.NodeBuilder.ClassNodeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds instances for class declarations in a syntax tree using Roslyn symbols.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.NodeBuilder.ConstructorNodeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds instances for constructor declarations in a syntax tree using Roslyn symbols.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.NodeBuilder.FieldNodeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds instances for field declarations in classes using Roslyn symbols.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.NodeBuilder.INodeBuilder
files.Summary: Defines a builder that creates graph nodes for a specific from Roslyn symbols and syntax.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.NodeBuilder.InterfaceNodeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds instances for interface declarations in a syntax tree using Roslyn symbols.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.NodeBuilder.MethodNodeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds instances for method declarations in classes using Roslyn symbols.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.NodeBuilder.PropertyNodeBuilder
files.Summary: Builds instances for property declarations using Roslyn symbols and captures referenced symbols inside property bodies.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.ClassNode
files.Summary: Represents a class in the code graph. Stores its Roslyn syntax, symbol, whether it is abstract, and its outgoing edges to related nodes (e.g. inheritance, implemented interfaces, members, etc.).

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.ConstructorNode
files.Summary: Represents a constructor in the code graph. Holds its Roslyn syntax, symbol, and outgoing edges to related nodes (e.g. created types, calls, or usage relationships).

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.EdgeNode
files.Summary: Represents a directed edge in the code graph. Connects a source node to a target node with a specific relationship type.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.EventNode
files.Summary: Represents an event in the code graph. Stores its Roslyn syntax wrapper, symbol, and outgoing edges to related nodes (e.g. handlers or containing types).

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.FieldNode
files.Summary: Represents a field in the code graph. Captures its Roslyn declaration and variable syntax, symbol, and outgoing edges to related nodes.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.IAnalyzerNode
files.Summary: Base interface for analyzer nodes that represent types (classes, interfaces, etc.) in the code graph. Provides access to the Roslyn type symbol, abstractness, and outgoing edges. This interface bunches the Class and Interface nodes together to handle them.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.INode
files.Summary: Base interface for all nodes in the code graph. Defines common properties for node type, Roslyn symbol, and outgoing edges to related nodes.

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.InterfaceNode
files.Summary: Represents an interface in the code graph. Stores its Roslyn syntax, symbol, and outgoing edges to related nodes (e.g. implemented classes).

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.MethodNode
files.Summary: Represents a method in the code graph. Stores its Roslyn syntax, symbol, return type, abstractness, and outgoing edges to related nodes (e.g. calls, usage, or return types).

files.Title: CodeAnalysisService.GraphService.Nodes.PropertyNode
files.Summary: Represents a property in the code graph. Captures its Roslyn syntax, symbol, referenced symbols (e.g. backing fields or accessed members), and outgoing edges.
